MINIGAME grid creatures 0.2

with sound!
move with WASD-+/touchscreen
aim and shoot with mouse/touchscreen

reqs: make
    linux?, SDL2, SDL2_mixer, OpenGL 3.0, GLEW.
    -or-
    android12+(3.1+): OpenGL ES 2.0+(w/VAO_ext), SDL2(android/jni/SDL2 and SDL2_mixer should link to your SDL2 source folders), android sdk, ndk, ant, java, ...?

android:
$ make droid

project names and descriptions are in :
    /android/AndroidManifest.xml
    /android/build.xml
    /android/makefile
app name:
    /android/res/values/strings.xml
screen prevented from sleeping in: 
    /android/src/org/libsdl/app/SDLActivity.java L:99
